data.description: Welcome to this remarkable townhome nestled in a serene location with picturesque views in Hunter’s Green. As you approach the property you will enter the beautifully landscaped  private courtyard with a pond, perfect for relaxing or enjoying some sun. When you enter the home you will immediately notice the pride of ownership and abundance of upgrades. The formal dining room features new light fixtures and opens up to the great room. The great room is stunning with a myriad of natural light. Exit through sliding doors to the covered and screened lanai. Designed with ample space and comfort in mind, this lanai provides an ideal setting to relax, entertain, and enjoy the natural beauty that surrounds the property. The beautifully updated kitchen features new counters, new cabinetry and stainless appliances. A spacious second bedroom on the first floor offers a walk in closet and a view of the rear pond and conservation. As you continue upstairs, you will first access the loft that overlooks the great room. Filled with natural light this loft can easily be converted to a third bedroom or office if desired. The master bedroom has plenty of storage including a walk-in closet and en suite bath that features dual sinks, updated cabinetry and a garden tub with separate shower. Throughout the home you will find new flooring and upgraded light fixtures. Community pool for this townhome community only.     Hunter’s Green:  Nestled in the heart of Tampa, Florida, Hunters Green community offers an exceptional living experience that captures the essence of luxury and convenience. This gold community boasts an array of world-class amenities, including a private golf course, tennis courts, sparkling swimming pools, fitness centers, and scenic nature trails. Residents revel in the meticulously manicured landscapes and the tranquil ambiance that permeates the neighborhood. The community's meticulously planned design ensures privacy and security, with gated entrances and 24/7 security personnel. With its close proximity to top-rated schools, shopping centers, and dining establishments, living in Hunters Green offers the perfect blend of exclusivity and accessibility. It's no wonder residents are captivated by the unparalleled lifestyle this esteemed community affords, making it the epitome of luxury living in Tampa.
